{"published time": "2024-11-15T05:45:50+08:00", "images": ["https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/feat-chile-2.webp"], "content": "<div class=\"post-thumbnail\">\n <img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"422\" sizes=\"(max-width: 448px) 100vw, 448px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/feat-chile-2.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/feat-chile-2.webp\" width=\"448\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n <div id=\"fb-root\">\n </div>\n <p>\n  As the newspaper El Pueblo reports, the \u2018Toma Dignidad\u2019 in La Florida, Chile, suffered an arson on 12\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  of November. Due to that, 60 houses were destroyed.\n </p>\n <p>\n  As it is denounced, the struggle of the residents for housing became stronger in the last years and they are combating and resisting the evictions. This is a problem for the State, specifically for the municipality of La Florida, which planned the eviction since some time ago and, as it is also denounced, would have used the old tactic of using thugs to set the fire.\n </p>\n <iframe allow=\"autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"767\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fperiodicoelpueblo2011%2Fposts%2Fpfbid0HF51iAh4S1RvtPRnSFAARDvUtZybrD8pAE1afMuQKEfsvwhJB9wyGtNyWQ6qZfJil&amp;width=500&amp;show_text=true&amp;height=767&amp;appId\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden\" width=\"500\">\n </iframe>\n <pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">Solidarity among the people flourished and several \u2018Tomas\u2019 already denounced the events. Among the ones which expressed solidarity with the \u2018Toma Dignidad\u2019 were the Coordinator of San Antonio \u2013 Cartagena, the Toma Cordillera from Puente Alto and the Toma 17 de Mayo from Cerro Navia who made a video denouncing the situation.</pre>\n <iframe allow=\"autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"1086\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Freel%2F1103085174748344&amp;width=500&amp;show_text=true&amp;height=1086&amp;appId\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden\" width=\"500\">\n </iframe>\n <iframe allow=\"autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"1086\" loading=\"lazy\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Freel%2F488947140134087%2F%3F__cft__[0]%3DAZULScUK44GapraZ9Kg3NbyLQfcrGxEEzT-19oivfAM0iSNFDW8wV5uxQmPhptr7F1Dxvn9qdMR4a4yekpqSsmSYabllA80YaQHGWZ2CYAfPO02YgUCjQx2i-7l2s8xeKMfzRZEPXXL-dZ9L_FgoARAr5NmTQKYZQgrMsV72BPe-OqivgV-Xarkxq1OSOZYAQjQ8lgb0vpDF4eLNKCz3wDVq%26__tn__%3D%252CO%252CP-R&amp;width=500&amp;show_text=true&amp;height=1086&amp;appId\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden\" width=\"500\">\n </iframe>\n</div>", "pdf_content": "", "pdf_links": [], "source": "https://redherald.org/2024/11/14/chile-in-face-of-the-new-arson-solidarity-and-struggle-flourish/", "type": "article", "title": "Chile: In face of the new arson, solidarity and struggle flourish! \u2013 The Red Herald", "description": "As the newspaper El Pueblo reports, the \u2018Toma Dignidad\u2019 in La Florida, Chile, suffered an arson on 12th of November. Due to that, 60 houses were destroyed.", "modified time": "2024-11-14T20:47:11+00:00", "author": ["F.W."], "categories": ["Featured", "The Americas"], "tags": ["Chile", "Housing", "Repression"], "sections": ["Featured", "The Americas", "Chile", "Housing", "Repression", "English"], "source_name": "Red Herald"}